Class CertificateMapperCfgDefn

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.forgerock.opendj.config.AbstractManagedObjectDefinition<C,​S>
      • org.forgerock.opendj.config.ManagedObjectDefinition<CertificateMapperCfgClient,​CertificateMapperCfg>
        • org.forgerock.opendj.server.config.meta.CertificateMapperCfgDefn
  • public final class CertificateMapperCfgDefn
extends ManagedObjectDefinition<CertificateMapperCfgClient,​CertificateMapperCfg>
    An interface for querying the Certificate Mapper managed object definition meta information.

    Certificate Mappers are responsible for establishing a mapping between a client certificate and the entry for the user that corresponds to that certificate.
